2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a deep learning framework for the task. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with motion features in addition to color features. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible sub-category as the paper proposes an efficient method for a challenging task in AI. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely sub-category, but still possible as the task of human pose estimation has applications in robotics.
